{"tid":1726390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動唔可以停 星期一黎明見","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T11:28:55.000Z","uid":1048,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc050d78321104698d8a9dcb9820dd1bddba4a3","tid":1726390,"uid":1048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"黎明行動係我地五個月打得好靚既一仗 <br />\n帶來影響最大 政府官都因為黎明行動要出嚟講嘢<br />\n依家咁多休息撚 分化撚 我地唔可以停止呢一樣對政府最有效既打擊 <br />\n<br />\n懇請大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一至五黎明行動 星期六日set deadline 政府唔回應就繼續黎明行動 直至政府答應五大訴求</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n最後 祝各弟妹<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武運昌隆</span></span>"},{"pid":"629c9c8cf374e52685450c563519c9de52c49d61","tid":1726390,"uid":1048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:51:04.000Z","msg":"大家一齊推返曬黎明行動po上去收鳩啲傻閪休息撚分化撚皮 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一打返上個星期既氣勢出嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"a94c812167e71bb2a39dbc97cfa417cf150d7607","tid":1726390,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:51:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a516e49bb301c218a4dd2a448da2b5a4103a671","tid":1726390,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"改下戰法<br />\n但唔休息！！！"},{"pid":"5bbb3a069a72651da592719d8a907305963bd46c","tid":1726390,"uid":1048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"可以轉打法 但我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不休息</span></span>"},{"pid":"2fa706e931a364af447818f0c0f5dbd210d839bd","tid":1726390,"uid":186640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:54:18.000Z","msg":"push!!"},{"pid":"0c8aabd64ed96649d04c5f4d82d95a90cdcd2f40","tid":1726390,"uid":1048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"推全部黎明行動po"},{"pid":"20bfc8c74b50a8031cba41d7